<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Highlightz Password Reset</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style type="text/css">
      /* Base Styles */
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        min-width: 100%;
        font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #FAFAFA;
        color: #333333;
      }
      .email-wrapper {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 20px auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      }
      /* Header */
      .email-header {
        background-color: #1a1a1a; /* Highlightz Dark Theme */
        padding: 30px;
        text-align: center;
        color: #ffffff;
      }
      .email-header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 26px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #FFD700; /* Gold accent for Highlightz */
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }
      /* Content Body */
      .email-body {
        padding: 40px 30px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      /* Reset Code Box */
      .reset-code-box {
        background-color: #fffdf0;
        border: 2px solid #FFD700;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 30px 0;
        text-align: center;
        border-radius: 8px;
      }
      .reset-code-box h2 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 36px;
        letter-spacing: 8px;
        color: #1a1a1a;
        font-family: 'Courier New', Courier, monospace;
      }
      /* Footer */
      .email-footer {
        background-color: #f6f6f6;
        padding: 24px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #777777;
      }
      .email-footer a {
        color: #FFD700;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <div class="email-header">
        <h1>Highlightz</h1>
      </div>
      
      <div class="email-body">
        <p style="font-size: 18px; margin-top: 0;">Hello <strong><%= user.name %></strong>,</p>
        <p>We received a request to reset the password for your <strong>Highlightz</strong> account. Use the code below to set up a new password:</p>
        
        <div class="reset-code-box">
          <h2><%= resetCode %></h2>
        </div>

        <p style="text-align: center; color: #666666; font-size: 14px;">
          This code is valid for the next <strong>10 minutes</strong>. 
          <br>For security, never share this code with anyone.
        </p>
        
        <p style="margin-top: 30px; border-top: 1px solid #eeeeee; padding-top: 20px; font-size: 14px; color: #999999;">
          If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="email-footer">
        <p>Need help? Contact our support at <a href="mailto:mirajhossen211013@gmail.com">mirajhossen211013@gmail.com</a></p>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Highlightz Platform</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>